{"tid":777543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣新北市醫院大火23人送院","createTime":"2018-08-13T03:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T04:04:13.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbcddec028cdfe1c87c4f6eeabd0e33af73f712e","tid":777543,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"台灣新北市醫院大火23人送院<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】台灣新北市新莊區一間醫院發生大火，23人送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n醫院七樓的位置可以見到有火光，現場冒出大量濃煙，有目擊者說聽到有爆炸聲。<br />\n<br />\n新北市消防部門凌晨四時許接報，派出二百多名消防員協助救火，救援人員忙於將病人疏散到醫院外，據報有14人無呼吸心跳，他們被分送到多間醫院，經搶救後當中最少4人仍然昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n消防員在約一個小時後將火救熄，初步調查顯示七樓病房首先起火，起火原因仍在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=316375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D316375&d=73UhWoOPSo7w239cqSuLYJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=94f69dcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D316375&h=5f77f6ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=316375</a>"},{"pid":"c43f47e41fda47e1c09d422b4f97bfc25d2c6916","tid":777543,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}